bilingual.source: My mother is a nurse in a hospital.
While the nurse examine him, she make some tea.
bilingual.target: 护士检查他时，她泡了些茶。

bilingual.source: The haughty nurse looked down her nose at the children.
bilingual.target: 傲慢的护士瞧不起孩子们。

bilingual.source: It marks the birthday of Florence Nightingale, a famous nurse.
bilingual.target: 它标志着著名护士弗洛伦斯·南丁格尔的生日。

bilingual.source: She decided to study nurse to become a nurse.
bilingual.target: 她决定学习护理，成为一名护士。

list.abstract: nurse（英 [nɜːs]，美 [nɜːrs]），英语单词，作名词时，为护士；护理员；沙锥齿鲨。作动词时，为治疗并护理；给…喂奶；哺乳。短语搭配有nursing home（养老院）。例句为“A girl was working as a nurse in a private hospital.（一个女孩在一家私立医院当护士。）” nurse不及物动词类近义词有cultivate、plant等，动词类近义词有fend for、attend on，名词类近义词有sister、amah。反义词有bottlefeed。

yingyinNormal.en: Suzy is wearing her nurse's costume.
yingyinNormal.zh: 苏西打扮成了护士的样子。

yingyinNormal.en: Suzy sheep is dressed up her nurse costume.
yingyinNormal.zh: 苏西羊正在穿她的护士套装。

yingyinNormal.en: The other nurse, Amber Vinson, continues to improve as well.
yingyinNormal.zh: 另一名护士，安伯.文森，也继续在康复过程中。

yingyinNormal.en: A robotic nurse?
yingyinNormal.zh: 机器人护士?

yingyinNormal.en: She wanted me to be a nurse. Get married, have three kids. Be a nurse.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她想让我当护士，结婚，生三个孩子，当护士。

yingyinNormal.en: Right there, nurse.
yingyinNormal.zh: 吻这儿就好，小护士。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm glad the nurse has arrived. Have you just come from the hospital? I'm not a real nurse. It's just pretend.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你很高兴这儿来了位护士，你刚从医院出来吗？我并不是一位真的护士，我只是扮成护士。

yingyinNormal.en: Will you do me a favor? Call that nurse. She's not a nurse. And you're not a S.H.I.E.L.D agent.
yingyinNormal.zh: 能帮我一个忙吗？去约那个护士。她不是护士。你也不是神盾局的特工。

yingyinNormal.en: Suzy, can I see your costume, please? I'm Nurse Suzy. I make people better. Very good, Nurse Suzy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 苏西，能让我仔细看一下你的装扮吗？我是苏西护士，我能减轻人们的病痛。非常好，苏西护士。

yingyinNormal.en: Hello, Suzy. Hello, Mr. Pig. I'm glad the nurse has arrived. Have you just come from the hospital? I'm not a real nurse. It's just pretend.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你好呀，苏西。你好呀，猪爸爸。很高兴这儿来了位护士，你刚从医院出来吗？我并不是一位真的护士，我只是扮成护士。

yingyinNormal.en: So, are you really gonna go out with that nurse man?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你真的要跟那个护士男约会？

yingyinNormal.en: I'm coming to see you. I'm going to wear my nurse's outfit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我来看你吧，我要穿我的护士装啦。

yingyinNormal.en: George. Richard. Nurse Suzy is here. And nurse Suzy says this is not dinosaur land. It's a hospital. And a hospital must be clean and tidy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治！理查德！苏西护士来了。苏西护士说，这里可不是恐龙乐园。而是一个医院，是医院的话，就必须保持干净和整洁。

yingyinNormal.en: Suzy, can I see your costume, please? I'm Nurse Suzy. I make people better. Very good, Nurse Suzy. Now, Danny. I'm a pirate. Shiver me timbers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 苏西，能让我仔细看一下你的装扮吗？我是苏西护士，我能减轻人们的病痛。非常好，苏西护士，换你了，丹尼。我是个海盗，你觉得怕了吧？

yingyinNormal.en: Hello, your majesty. I'm Nurse Suzy. Open wide and say "ahhh".
yingyinNormal.zh: 你好呀，佩奇公主，我是护士苏西，嘴巴张大，然后说阿。

yingyinNormal.en: Suzy sheep is dressed up her nurse costume. Don't worry. I'm only a pretend nurse. Stick your tongue out and say Ah. Ah.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小羊苏西穿上了他的护士制服。别担心。我只是假扮的而已。把你的舌头伸出来。啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Suzy sheep is dressed up in her nurse costume. Don't worry. I'm only a pretend nurse. Stick your tongue out and say Ah. Ah.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小羊苏西穿上了他的护士制服。别担心。我只是假扮的而已。把你的舌头伸出来。啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Later, when I started feeling better, the nurse came in and she called me a fighter.
yingyinNormal.zh: 过了一会，我感觉好点了，护士进来说我很勇敢。

yingyinNormal.en: You have to be the mother, the father, the mediator, the nurse, the cool uncle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你要又当爹又当妈，还有调停者,护士,还有怪蜀黍。

yingyinNormal.en: Hello, your majesty. I'm Nurse Suzy. Open wide and say "ahhh". "Ahhh".
yingyinNormal.zh: 你好呀，佩琪公主，我是护士苏西，嘴巴张大，然后说阿。阿。
